## Running the loop

The one-command verification loop for this family is `just verify-tcps`: it runs the
consumer's evidence emitter (`examples/tcps-generated/scripts/verify.sh` — real cargo
checks emitting `ver:` facts), then `ggen sync run` under `ggen-verify-pack`'s five
refusal gates, then `ggen receipt verify` — see the `verify-tcps` recipe in `justfile`
(including its disclosed re-lock limitation).

